## Technical

Postgresql
- postgres18.oursky.dev (Thanks Big Cal)

## Technical

Build on k8s
- Buildkit
- [https://github.com/moby/buildkit](https://github.com/moby/buildkit)

Limitation
- No replicas
  - No time study make it works
- Too many build job will lead to service oom

## Technical

Redis
- Kvrocks
- [https://kvrocks.apache.org/](https://kvrocks.apache.org/)
- Support multi users via namespace
  - https://kvrocks.apache.org/docs/namespace
- Redis API but use RocksDB as storage
  - slower in speed but not eating rams $$

## Technical

S3
- RustFS
- [https://rustfs.com/](https://rustfs.com/)
- minio alternative :0)
- Just want to try try

